  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/c22f80514ab3c177339d936d68c5690a.poster.avif?t=1766456074\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/c22f80514ab3c177339d936d68c5690a.webm?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/c22f80514ab3c177339d936d68c5690a.mp4?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drift a missile through unique and punishingly difficult asteroid fields in order to intercept and destroy incoming meteors. Remember though, competition is fierce on the leaderboards, so speed and precision are paramount!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/0265aa423def3472020614cadff72a97.avif?t=1766456074\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/882d931ff52ebc20fe000a8babb39566.poster.avif?t=1766456074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/882d931ff52ebc20fe000a8babb39566.webm?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/882d931ff52ebc20fe000a8babb39566.mp4?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operating the ISJ-10 might seem straightforward at first glance, but perfecting its movement is the real challenge. So buckle up and prepare to sharpen your skills - you will die a lot! But don't worry, the Command Center is well-stocked with missiles, making failure just a routine part of the business. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/a9af514fc8d4c9d5dcf19494da571c07.avif?t=1766456074\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/e6f2193684324e7de2ede895de40ab1e.poster.avif?t=1766456074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/e6f2193684324e7de2ede895de40ab1e.webm?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/e6f2193684324e7de2ede895de40ab1e.mp4?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills drifting the ISJ-10 across 2 unique game modes and 25+ challenging levels. Be warned, though, every mode has its own demands and each level is more punishing than the last. It will take precision, determination, and grit in order to complete your mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/e97f3952f8fa7f1f90b4d32d0a6ab52f.avif?t=1766456074\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/076f42d16ded2800ae6e60382f7bdb67.poster.avif?t=1766456074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/076f42d16ded2800ae6e60382f7bdb67.webm?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/076f42d16ded2800ae6e60382f7bdb67.mp4?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command Center Earth has been designed from the start to be easy to get into and easy to get out of. With zero loading screens, the game seamlessly transitions from menus to action at the click of a button. Waiting for a few friends to join your lobby? Why not attempt to beat Yuma for the 25th time?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/7607adc82be334023ec1dcf9de21f1e5.avif?t=1766456074\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/9bf2d2aae4114bc66d7d87c23164372d.poster.avif?t=1766456074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/9bf2d2aae4114bc66d7d87c23164372d.webm?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/9bf2d2aae4114bc66d7d87c23164372d.mp4?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level & level mode has been painstakingly crafted to ensure players can compete on a high stakes leaderboard. No matter where you play, each level runs exactly the same, fully deterministic across machines! Find a small passage through a few meteors that no one's discovered? If your skills allow it, reap the benefits and shave seconds off your leaderboard time!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/c22f80514ab3c177339d936d68c5690a.poster.avif?t=1766456074\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/c22f80514ab3c177339d936d68c5690a.webm?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/c22f80514ab3c177339d936d68c5690a.mp4?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drift a missile through unique and punishingly difficult asteroid fields in order to intercept and destroy incoming meteors. Remember though, competition is fierce on the leaderboards, so speed and precision are paramount!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/0265aa423def3472020614cadff72a97.avif?t=1766456074\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/882d931ff52ebc20fe000a8babb39566.poster.avif?t=1766456074\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/882d931ff52ebc20fe000a8babb39566.webm?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2639860/extras/882d931ff52ebc20fe000a8babb39566.mp4?t=1766456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operating the ISJ-10 might seem s